  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle npm fails to install\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nGet the latest version of node; 11.10.0\r\nthen type: sudo npm install -g truffle\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nInstall the package\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n```\r\nsudo  npm install npm@latest -g\r\nPassword:\r\n/usr/local/bin/npm -> /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npm-cli.js\r\n/usr/local/bin/npx -> /usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npx-cli.js\r\n+ npm@6.9.0\r\nupdated 1 package in 8.893s\r\nX-MBP-3:eth_smart_contract X$ sudo npm install -g truffle\r\n/usr/local/bin/truffle -> /usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js\r\n\r\n> truffle@5.0.24 postinstall /usr/local/lib/node_modules/truffle\r\n> node ./scripts/postinstall.js\r\n\r\nshell-init: error retrieving current directory: getcwd: cannot access parent directories: Permission denied\r\npath.js:1077\r\n        path = process.cwd();\r\n                       ^\r\n\r\nError: EACCES: permission denied, uv_cwd\r\n    at Object.resolve (path.js:1077:24)\r\n    at internal/main/run_main_module.js:9:24\r\n```\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n$uname -a\r\nDarwin X-MacBook-Pro-3.local 16.7.0 Darwin Kernel Version 16.7.0: Sun Oct 28 22:30:19 PDT 2018; root:xnu-3789.73.27~1/RELEASE_X86_64 x86_64\r\n\r\n$ node -v\r\nv11.10.0\r\n\r\n$ npm -v\r\n6.9.0\r\n",
